Build an enterprise-grade AWS Security Dashboard platform using:

Frontend:
- React for the complete UI/dashboard experience.

Backend:
- Python for AWS integrations, findings processing, report generation, scheduling, email orchestration, and automation workflows.

Goal:
Create a premium, visually stunning, executive-level AWS Security Dashboard for centralized organization-wide security posture management.

Environment Context:
- AWS Security services are enabled organization-wide through a delegated administrator account.
- There are 82 AWS accounts under the AWS Organization.
- AWS Inspector and CSPM are enabled organization-wide.
- Delegated access and IAM functionality are already configured and working.
- The application will run on an EC2 instance outside the delegated account.
- The platform must later support Docker deployment.
- Do not redesign delegated account permissions.

Core Requirement:
The system must centrally collect findings from the delegated account, process findings for all AWS accounts, generate professional reports, and automatically distribute findings to account owners.

